<p>
<note n="0802b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0802b02">此言蓮宗之信心稱性而行也</note>
<note n="0803b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0803b01">此言蓮宗之止觀稱性而行也</note>
<note n="0803b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0803b02">三德三身三觀總是一心且舉一具三言三即一可以互論非定屬何等也</note>
<note n="0803b03" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0803b03">依正非異者言依報正報皆有三觀也</note>
<note n="0803b04" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0803b04">此言蓮宗之六度稱性而行也</note>
<note n="0803b05" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0803b05">此言蓮宗之悲願稱性而行也</note>
<note n="0804b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0804b01">知恩分者云知功德之恩分量無邊也欲心修功德之心也</note>
<note n="0804b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0804b02">此言能稱法性而行則一念攝諸佛淨土也</note>
</p>
